BUG REPORT #2

There is a bug in the village card in the cardEffect function in dominion.c

Village is giving the wrong number of actions.

Severity: Medium. Causes incorrect gameplay, but does not interrupt the game.

Priority: Low. Problem only occurs if this card is played.

BUG REPORT #3

There is a bug in the ambassador card in the cardEffect function in dominion.c

In certain cases when running tests, the ambassador card has an infinite loop.

Severity: High. Causes incorrect gameplay, interrupts the game.

Priority: Medium. Problem only occurs if this card is played.
